# Data Licenses

The example data included in this directory is sourced from publicly available
datasets released under permissive licenses.

## Audio

| Dataset | License | URL |
|---------|---------|-----|
| LibriTTS-R | CC BY 4.0 | https://www.openslr.org/141/ |
| LibriHeavy | CC BY 4.0 | https://github.com/k2-fsa/libriheavy |
| SLUE Phase-2 SQA5 | CC BY-SA 4.0 | https://huggingface.co/datasets/asapp/slue-phase-2 |
| atomic10x | CC BY 4.0 | https://huggingface.co/datasets/allenai/atomic |
| AI-Hub Korean speech example data | AI-Hub 이용정책 / 데이터 이용정책 | https://www.aihub.or.kr/ |

## Notes

Some full-duplex training examples include in-house synthesized audio generated using Qwen3-TTS.
